10
00:01:33,799 --> 00:01:34,480
Perfect.

11
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,920
The Prince Xian has turned into a demon.

12
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,400
He'll be useful to me.

13
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,280
Your Highness.

14
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:52,719
Let's go.

15
00:02:00,359 --> 00:02:01,079
Your Highness.

16
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:02,079
Let's take a break.

17
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:07,680
Your Highness.

18
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,799
Are you feeling better?

19
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,039
Now that I'm a demon,

20
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,039
