21
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,319
I know

22
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,400
your current appearance

23
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,960
is due to Meng Li.

24
00:02:19,479 --> 00:02:21,240
The demon hunter came to your mansion

25
00:02:21,319 --> 00:02:22,520
after receiving a secret report.

26
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,560
I believe

27
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:25,439
it's the demon girl's trick.

28
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,800
Your Highness, don't worry.

29
00:02:30,439 --> 00:02:32,199
Even if you're forced to be a demon,

30
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,360
I believe

31
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,360
your heart of protecting the right

32
00:02:35,879 --> 00:02:37,000
will never change.

33
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:55,360
Of course.

34
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:58,560
I won't allow demons to disturb the world.

35
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,319
But the demon said

36
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:03,039
the sorcery

37
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,599
is irreversible.

38
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,840
My current form

39
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,360
