40
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:10,719
Your Highness,

41
00:03:11,159 --> 00:03:12,240
it's not entirely impossible

42
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,199
to return to human form.

43
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:17,000
I know a way to reverse the sorcery.

44
00:03:19,479 --> 00:03:22,199
If we can kill the witch who turned you,

45
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,000
the sorcery can be undone,

46
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:26,639
and you'll regain your human form.

47
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:54,840
Rumor has it

48
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,439
that Chi Xin has been collecting

49
00:03:57,439 --> 00:04:00,039
and has gathered most of the pieces,

50
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:00,879
melding them into one.

51
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:04,159
Now only the most crucial fragment remains,

52
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,800
known as

53
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,639
the Water Cloud Rhinoceros.

54
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,639
Where is it?

55
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:12,319
There's a Brush Demon on Rhinoceros Moon Mountain

56
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:14,199
