57
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:19,759
You must be the legendary Brush Demon.

58
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,120
Indeed,

59
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:22,839
I am You Wencai.

60
00:04:23,199 --> 00:04:24,120
I know you.

61
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,120
Dream-Eating Demon,

62
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:25,959
Meng Li.

63
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,040
I've heard so much about you.

64
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:29,920
I came to visit you.

65
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,040
Then...

66
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:33,959
Tell me,

67
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:35,639
what do the legends say about me?

68
00:04:35,639 --> 00:04:37,120
Are they

69
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,000
all full of

70
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,120
praises?

71
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,680
The legends say

72
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,000
you're a walking encyclopedia,

73
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:43,279
and all-knowing.

74
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:48,120
That's a fair assessment.

75
00:04:49,839 --> 00:04:51,160
I've come to seek your help

76
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,319
with something important.

77
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,800
You've made the effort to come here

78
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:57,839
and said some nice things about me.

79
00:04:57,879 --> 00:04:58,680
I can help you,

80
00:04:58,959 --> 00:04:59,439
but

81
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,759
I have my own rules.

82
00:05:02,199 --> 00:05:04,399
You must fulfill a wish for me,

83
00:05:04,399 --> 00:05:05,600
