85
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:07,319
What do you say?

86
00:05:07,639 --> 00:05:08,680
I will do my best.

87
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,800
It's actually quite simple.

88
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:13,360
I need a couple to help me.

89
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:14,439
Young lady,

90
00:05:16,199 --> 00:05:17,160
