91
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,319
Call him over.

92
00:05:21,959 --> 00:05:23,000
I don't have a lover.

93
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,000
I know everything

94
00:05:26,199 --> 00:05:27,639
