95
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:29,319
You clearly have a lover.

96
00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:30,800
Don't try to deceive me.

97
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:31,959
My Lady.

98
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,480
My Lady.

99
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,199
You are so cruel.

100
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:38,959
We just had a quarrel,

101
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:41,240
but you abandoned me.

102
00:05:42,279 --> 00:05:43,240
Why are you here?

103
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,120
It's not impossible

104
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:49,040
for Your Highness to turn back.

105
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:53,360
This object can track people

106
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:55,279
and help you kill Meng Li.

107
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,360
This object is clearly Xu Qinglai's.

108
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,639
But it's in her hand.

109
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:04,560
Mu Feishuang has been acting strange.

110
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,360
We must be cautious.

111
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,680
The best course of action now

112
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,079
is to revert to human form as soon as possible,

113
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,199
then we'll decide on the next steps.

114
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:10,959
Alright,

115
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,240
thank you for your help.

116
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,079
I'll do it.

117
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:29,959
I'll do it.

118
00:06:29,959 --> 00:06:32,399
Of course, to make amends to you.

119
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,920
It was my fault.

120
00:06:34,319 --> 00:06:35,160
My lady,

121
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,639
don't be mad at me.

122
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:38,680
Who's your wife?

123
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:40,480
We're not familiar with each other.

124
00:06:40,879 --> 00:06:42,399
My dear, don't be mad at me.

125
00:06:43,199 --> 00:06:44,120
We two

126
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,879
spend every day together.

127
00:06:46,399 --> 00:06:47,600
Except for loving couples,

128
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:51,360
who else can be so close

129
00:06:52,279 --> 00:06:53,680
and can't be separated for a moment?

130
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:54,879
Shen Que,

131
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,360
am I too kind to you?

132
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,439
You even say such absurd words.

133
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:01,800
Do you really think I won't hurt you?

134
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:07,439
Hey.

135
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,399
Are you really a couple?

136
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,439
You don't look like it.

137
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:13,560
Hey.

138
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,360
Please wait a moment.

139
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,839
We often

140
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:18,879
have little quarrels.

141
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,920
My wife is still angry.

142
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,879
I'll go apologize to her.

143
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,480
You want something from the Brush Demon?

144
00:07:33,759 --> 00:07:34,560
Well,

145
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,240
I have questions for him too.

146
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:37,560
How about

147
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:39,240
we join forces

148
00:07:39,519 --> 00:07:40,680
to break the formation?

149
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,480
This is a win-win situation.

150
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:44,160
Why not?

151
00:07:44,279 --> 00:07:46,759
Didn't you always despise demons?

152
00:07:46,879 --> 00:07:48,199
How could you now

153
00:07:48,439 --> 00:07:49,319
seek their help?

154
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:50,800
A gentleman should be

155
00:07:50,959 --> 00:07:52,240
flexible in life.

156
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,879
Besides, you've turned me into a demon.

157
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:56,720
What's wrong

158
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,240
with asking for help?

159
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,439
So, what do you want to know?

160
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:02,560
If you want to become human again,

161
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,720
I advise you

162
00:08:03,959 --> 00:08:05,240
to give up on that idea.

163
00:08:05,439 --> 00:08:06,279
What I want

164
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:07,519
is my own business.

165
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,360
If you don't want to cooperate,

166
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,639
I'm afraid your goal

167
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,639
will be delayed, right?

168
00:08:17,639 --> 00:08:18,759
Besides,

169
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:21,800
I just want you to pretend to be my lover.

170
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:22,839
What?

171
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:25,560
You dare not?

172
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:38,159
Since you are so sincere,

173
00:08:38,639 --> 00:08:39,960
I'll forgive you

174
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,240
for old times' sake.

175
00:08:41,399 --> 00:08:42,639
But I hope you won't

176
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,639
make the same mistake again.

177
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,480
You're right.

178
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:48,240
From now on,

179
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:50,480
I won't make you angry anymore.

180
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,279
Even if you hit me

181
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,000
or scold me,

182
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:56,080
I'll take it as your concern for me.

183
00:08:56,559 --> 00:08:57,360
Then I'll

184
00:08:57,679 --> 00:09:00,240
take good care of you.

185
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:06,320
Are you sure you're lovers?

186
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:08,120
Why does it look so weird?

187
00:09:08,519 --> 00:09:09,360
Of course.

188
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,080
We've been entangled for two lifetimes.

189
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,000
Genuine and authentic.

190
00:09:12,399 --> 00:09:14,360
Love is stronger than gold.

191
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:17,480
Please help me fulfill my wish.

192
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,240
After it's done,

193
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,279
I'll tell you everything

194
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:20,919
you want to know, okay?

195
00:09:20,919 --> 00:09:22,200
What do you need us to do?

196
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,080
I may be famous

197
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,360
and respected,

198
00:09:28,039 --> 00:09:29,480
but for centuries,

199
00:09:29,639 --> 00:09:32,159
I've been writing nothing but

200
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:33,200
boring

201
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,480
historical records.

202
00:09:34,559 --> 00:09:35,600
I...

203
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:39,120
I love romance novels.

204
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:41,720
They're all the same,

205
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,879
always about rescuing women in distress.

206
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:44,639
It makes my head

207
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:45,720
ache just reading them.

208
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:46,960
So,

209
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,200
I want to write a novel

210
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:51,080
that opens the eyes of future generations.

211
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:53,799
But I've been stuck on one part for years.

212
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:54,639
Would you two

213
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,120
be willing to help me?

214
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,039
How can we help?

215
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:58,559
Oh,

216
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:01,600
I'll put you two into my novel.

217
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,480
You just need to resolve the crisis

218
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:05,200
and write a perfect ending.

219
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,039
It's not difficult.

220
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:06,960
I, Meng Li,

221
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,519
will do my best to help you.

222
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,279
Oh.

223
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:13,799
Please rest assured.

224
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:16,039
We will do our best.

225
00:10:16,519 --> 00:10:17,399
Good.

226
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:19,799
Now,

227
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:23,279
you two enter

228
00:10:23,519 --> 00:10:25,320
the formation.

229
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:28,840
[The protagonists in the scroll are a couple.]

230
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:30,360
[They love each other deeply,]

231
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,679
[and vow to be together forever.]

232
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,879
[But their love never lasts,]

233
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:36,679
[always ending in eternal separation.]

234
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,759
I advise you to see the situation clearly

235
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:09,080
and avoid pointless actions.

236
00:11:09,279 --> 00:11:10,720
Such a good opportunity,

237
00:11:10,919 --> 00:11:12,159
how could I waste it?

238
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:14,000
Then let's settle this with our abilities.

239
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,919
Now that we've both lost our powers,

240
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,840
if it comes down to hand-to-hand,

241
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,679
you won't have any advantage.

242
00:11:20,039 --> 00:11:21,240
If you beg me,

243
00:11:21,679 --> 00:11:23,720
I might spare your life

244
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:25,320
for old times' sake.

245
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:34,480
Your words are sharp,

246
00:11:34,799 --> 00:11:37,440
but your actions are slow.

247
00:11:41,799 --> 00:11:42,519
Alas,

248
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:44,279
this isn't how I wanted it to end.

249
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:45,240
Let's start over.

250
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:57,440
Sneaking from behind is cowardly.

251
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,360
Don't you feel ashamed?

252
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,559
I've lost all my power.

253
00:12:00,559 --> 00:12:01,519
