254
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,480
Aren't you the one who should feel ashamed?

255
00:12:03,559 --> 00:12:05,039
That's because I'm honorable and upright.

256
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:07,440
Your Highness, please use your brain.

257
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:09,039
See the current situation clearly.

258
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,919
If we do something inappropriate,

259
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:12,559
the story time will reverse,

260
00:12:12,559 --> 00:12:14,200
and the story will start over.

261
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,519
It must be that old man.

262
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:20,240
You evil spirits are all so despicable.

263
00:12:22,039 --> 00:12:23,519
Why are you cursing yourself?

264
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:28,159
If you two break free from the romantic story,

265
00:12:28,159 --> 00:12:30,200
you'll be trapped in the book forever,

266
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:32,039
repeating the same cycle,

267
00:12:32,039 --> 00:12:34,120
never able to escape.

268
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:37,639
Shen Que,

269
00:12:38,159 --> 00:12:39,240
if that's the case,

270
00:12:39,399 --> 00:12:40,360
why don't we

271
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:42,000
follow You Wencai's demands

272
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:42,960
and continue the story?

273
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:43,840
Let's get out of the book first,

274
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:44,679
what do you say?

275
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:46,759
Fine.

276
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,679
The current plot is

277
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,360
you saved me from danger.

278
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:54,519
That means we are being hunted.

279
00:12:55,279 --> 00:12:56,759
It's getting dark.

280
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,559
We should find a place to hide

281
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,480
to ensure our safety.

282
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:03,679
That's what I want.
